                    <button class="btn btn-evidence" onclick="showEvidence()" style="padding: 8px 16px; margin: 0 10px; font-size: 14px;">ğŸ“‹ è¨¼æ‹ å“ã‚’ã¤ãã¤ã‘ã‚‹</button>
                    <button class="nav-btn" id="next-btn" onclick="nextTestimony()">æ¬¡ â–¶</button>
                </div>
            </div>

